x; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">Executives at Kerin=
g, for their part, have publicly acknowledged that they were impacted <i>di=
sproportionately </i>in China=E2=80=94and that these sales declines, exacer=
bated by other macroeconomic issues, limited their ability to support the D=
e Sarno project until recently. <b>Armelle Poulou</b>, the group=E2=80=99s =
